
### faker.providers.address

	fake.state()                                                                                # Maryland
	fake.random_letter()                                                                        # e
	fake.postcode()                                                                             # 97055
	fake.country()                                                                              # Ukraine
	fake.random_digit_not_null()                                                                # 7
	fake.random_element(elements=('a', 'b', 'b'))                                               # b
	fake.secondary_address()                                                                    # Suite 849
	fake.country_code()                                                                         # MH
	fake.lexify(text="????")                                                                    # pGHv
	fake.random_int(min=0, max=9999)                                                            # 6693
	fake.numerify(text="###")                                                                   # 478
	fake.address()                                                                              # 07480 Graham Unions
	                                                                                              North Bartonbury, WV 05968-3639
	fake.longitude()                                                                            # -132.630000
	fake.building_number()                                                                      # 8062
	fake.random_number(digits=None)                                                             # 9707057
	fake.city_suffix()                                                                          # port
	fake.latitude()                                                                             # -4.4862335
	fake.postalcode()                                                                           # 48611
	fake.postalcode_plus4()                                                                     # 01587-7077
	fake.randomize_nb_elements(number=10, le=False, ge=False)                                   # 7
	fake.street_name()                                                                          # Brekke Burg
	fake.military_apo()                                                                         # PSC 6206, Box 0972
	fake.military_ship()                                                                        # USCGC
	fake.street_address()                                                                       # 8560 Skyler Cliff Apt. 779
	fake.city_prefix()                                                                          # South
	fake.zipcode()                                                                              # 55620
	fake.state_abbr()                                                                           # WA
	fake.city()                                                                                 # DuBuqueberg
	fake.geo_coordinate(center=None, radius=0.001)                                              # 178.290206
	fake.bothify(text="## ??")                                                                  # 32 mk
	fake.street_suffix()                                                                        # Ports
	fake.military_state()                                                                       # AA
	fake.random_digit()                                                                         # 2
	fake.zipcode_plus4()                                                                        # 99217-4530
	fake.military_dpo()                                                                         # Unit 2828 Box 8203

### faker.providers.barcode

	fake.ean8()                                                                                 # 45586903
	fake.ean13()                                                                                # 9767858774118
	fake.ean(length=13)                                                                         # 2219912573092

### faker.providers.color

	fake.color_name()                                                                           # Purple
	fake.safe_color_name()                                                                      # olive
	fake.rgb_css_color()                                                                        # rgb(113,240,220)
	fake.hex_color()                                                                            # #b10a36
	fake.rgb_color()                                                                            # 197,168,34
	fake.safe_hex_color()                                                                       # #88bb00
	fake.rgb_color_list()                                                                       # (216, 115, 206)

### faker.providers.company

	fake.company()                                                                              # Kuhic-Anderson
	fake.company_suffix()                                                                       # Inc
	fake.bs()                                                                                   # streamline revolutionary markets
	fake.catch_phrase()                                                                         # Multi-lateral human-resource encryption

### faker.providers.credit_card

	fake.credit_card_security_code(card_type=None)                                              # 507
	fake.credit_card_full(card_type=None)                                                       # Diners Club / Carte Blanche
	                                                                                              Brittany Jerde
	                                                                                              30505618606745 07/23
	                                                                                              CVC: 351
	fake.credit_card_provider(card_type=None)                                                   # Mastercard
	fake.credit_card_number(card_type=None)                                                     # 30218341327031
	fake.credit_card_expire(start="now", end="+10y", date_format="%m/%y")                       # 03/23

### faker.providers.currency

	fake.currency_code()                                                                        # KRW

### faker.providers.date_time

	fake.date_time_this_year(before_now=True, after_now=False)                                  # 2015-08-14 21:42:40
	fake.time(pattern="%H:%M:%S")                                                               # 18:05:22
	fake.am_pm()                                                                                # PM
	fake.date_time_between_dates(datetime_start=None, datetime_end=None)                        # 2015-10-24 16:16:25
	fake.date_time_ad()                                                                         # 0670-10-26 05:42:49
	fake.day_of_week()                                                                          # Wednesday
	fake.date_time_this_decade(before_now=True, after_now=False)                                # 2012-12-02 19:48:17
	fake.month()                                                                                # 01
	fake.day_of_month()                                                                         # 25
	fake.date_time()                                                                            # 2014-11-28 04:22:47
	fake.century()                                                                              # V
	fake.month_name()                                                                           # May
	fake.iso8601()                                                                              # 1992-09-19T11:42:44
	fake.date_time_this_century(before_now=True, after_now=False)                               # 2012-09-13 01:31:33
	fake.year()                                                                                 # 1979
	fake.date_time_between(start_date="-30y", end_date="now")                                   # 1992-02-07 21:51:20
	fake.date(pattern="%Y-%m-%d")                                                               # 1972-09-02
	fake.time_delta()                                                                           # 10785 days, 0:30:50
	fake.date_time_this_month(before_now=True, after_now=False)                                 # 2015-10-07 17:10:53
	fake.timezone()                                                                             # America/Argentina/Rio_Gallegos
	fake.unix_time()                                                                            # 958312262

### faker.providers.file

	fake.file_name(category=None, extension=None)                                               # incidunt.mp3
	fake.mime_type(category=None)                                                               # multipart/signed
	fake.file_extension(category=None)                                                          # html

### faker.providers.internet

	fake.ipv6()                                                                                 # 7d59:f726:94e2:820c:b401:8bfd:b55c:dfdc
	fake.slug(*args, **kwargs)                                                                  # exercitationem
	fake.uri_path(deep=None)                                                                    # tag
	fake.free_email_domain()                                                                    # hotmail.com
	fake.uri_extension()                                                                        # .html
	fake.free_email()                                                                           # schuppe.chelsi@gmail.com
	fake.company_email()                                                                        # vincenza.simonis@lakinschuppe.com
	fake.mac_address()                                                                          # a4:b3:3f:ac:fe:6c
	fake.safe_email()                                                                           # crowe@example.net
	fake.image_url(width=None, height=None)                                                     # http://www.lorempixel.com/519/776
	fake.user_name(*args, **kwargs)                                                             # dkuvalis
	fake.uri_page()                                                                             # homepage
	fake.ipv4()                                                                                 # 41.196.231.114
	fake.tld()                                                                                  # biz
	fake.domain_word(*args, **kwargs)                                                           # cole
	fake.domain_name()                                                                          # waters.com
	fake.url()                                                                                  # http://mcdermott.com/
	fake.uri()                                                                                  # http://www.kirlin.biz/wp-content/main/blog/post/
	fake.email()                                                                                # blake21@gmail.com

### faker.providers.job

	fake.job()                                                                                  # Engineer, automotive

### faker.providers.lorem

	fake.word()                                                                                 # et
	fake.paragraph(nb_sentences=3, variable_nb_sentences=True)                                  # Nulla soluta vitae dolores et ut. Sint autem id ipsam. Cul
	                                                                                              pa aut rerum ut vel velit ullam vel. Quia deleniti ullam d
	                                                                                              olorum non ab est. Fuga delectus corporis sapiente sit per
	                                                                                              ferendis aut quo.
	fake.sentence(nb_words=6, variable_nb_words=True)                                           # Voluptas iusto nisi dolore omnis et voluptatibus.
	fake.sentences(nb=3)                                                                        # ['Aut dignissimos impedit dicta sed unde.', 'Quis nulla es
	                                                                                              se in ut.', 'Et sapiente iusto deleniti sit et maxime sit.
	                                                                                              ']
	fake.text(max_nb_chars=200)                                                                 # Id sunt magnam quo tenetur corporis. Aut quis aperiam et r
	                                                                                              eiciendis eos. Et quia consequuntur ipsam sit reprehenderi
	                                                                                              t. Cupiditate corporis sed molestiae dolorum.
	fake.paragraphs(nb=3)                                                                       # ['Et minus sapiente qui autem. Aliquid nostrum velit earum
	                                                                                               accusamus blanditiis aliquam corporis. Quo expedita et iu
	                                                                                              re. Veritatis non molestiae est fugit expedita eligendi ni
	                                                                                              hil.', 'Ut alias nulla quisquam sapiente. Qui velit sed id
	                                                                                               consectetur officiis. Et et enim est voluptatibus officia
	                                                                                              .', 'Dolore quaerat aspernatur ratione similique nam rerum
	                                                                                               sint. Est et ut voluptatem aliquam quam sint. Unde aut fu
	                                                                                              giat minus aut sint id vitae. Quia ducimus perspiciatis qu
	                                                                                              ae repellendus perferendis odio quis.']
	fake.words(nb=3)                                                                            # ['et', 'similique', 'qui']

### faker.providers.misc

	fake.boolean(chance_of_getting_true=50)                                                     # True
	fake.sha256(raw_output=False)                                                               # a308979d123f1918c638ce1fde55317647f066473bfdab482b6d4a9706
	                                                                                              659b85
	fake.md5(raw_output=False)                                                                  # a017d2b7adfcb777b0e99a698ee69f72
	fake.null_boolean()                                                                         # None
	fake.password(length=10, special_chars=True, digits=True, upper_case=True, lower_case=True) # f*GHgq^P%S
	fake.sha1(raw_output=False)                                                                 # 8aa71d8c8d2bd29ea019a3ad9aa54546c588ba11
	fake.language_code()                                                                        # el
	fake.uuid4()                                                                                # f39c8a33-5807-4037-99c0-c62ffd4a71f0
	fake.locale()                                                                               # ru_SM

### faker.providers.date_time

### faker.providers.date_time

	fake.date_time_this_decade(before_now=True, after_now=False)                                # 2012-07-09 23:28:10
	fake.month()                                                                                # 04
	fake.day_of_month()                                                                         # 30
	fake.date_time()                                                                            # 2008-08-02 11:19:30
	fake.century()                                                                              # XIV
	fake.month_name()                                                                           # March
	fake.iso8601()                                                                              # 1978-02-13T12:09:06

	fake.year()                                                                                 # 2007
	fake.date_time_between(start_date="-30y", end_date="now")                                   # 2013-06-29 07:46:27
	fake.date(pattern="%Y-%m-%d")                                                               # 1983-02-17
	fake.time_delta()                                                                           # 4245 days, 7:47:16

	fake.timezone()                                                                             # Asia/Colombo
	fake.unix_time()                                                                            # 279908027

### faker.providers.lorem

	fake.text(max_nb_chars=200)                                                                 # Assumenda sunt qui doloribus corporis. Nobis ipsa eum a qu

### faker.providers.date_time

	fake.time(pattern="%H:%M:%S")                                                               # 20:49:12
	fake.am_pm()                                                                                # AM
	fake.date_time_between_dates(datetime_start=None, datetime_end=None)                        # 2015-10-24 16:16:26
	fake.date_time_ad()                                                                         # 1084-05-29 08:03:54
	fake.day_of_week()                                                                          # Friday
	fake.date_time_this_decade(before_now=True, after_now=False)                                # 2011-12-25 14:52:28
	fake.month()                                                                                # 02
	fake.day_of_month()                                                                         # 11
	fake.date_time()                                                                            # 2011-05-13 14:16:14
	fake.century()                                                                              # XVI
	fake.month_name()                                                                           # August
	fake.iso8601()                                                                              # 1972-12-13T19:56:23
	fake.date_time_this_century(before_now=True, after_now=False)                               # 2015-05-02 03:43:05
	fake.year()                                                                                 # 1970
	fake.date_time_between(start_date="-30y", end_date="now")                                   # 2000-09-18 16:40:14
	fake.date(pattern="%Y-%m-%d")                                                               # 2000-03-27
	fake.time_delta()                                                                           # 15970 days, 11:53:11
	fake.date_time_this_month(before_now=True, after_now=False)                                 # 2015-10-18 23:38:26
	fake.timezone()                                                                             # Africa/Ndjamena
	fake.unix_time()                                                                            # 846379520

	fake.unix_time()                                                                            # 989636714
